<ITEM>71. Ca&s;tantin filius Wrgui&s;t xxx. v.<NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">Sic. &s;ed chronologia tantum xxx. patitur, ut Inne&s;ius habe <HI>v.</HI> forte &s;ignificat <HI>vere</HI> vel <HI>vero,</HI> nam dividitur &agrave; xxx. Secundum Tighernacum et Annal Ulton. Con&s;tantinus regnat ab A. 789 ad 819, hoc e&s;t 30 annis.</NOTE> an. reg.</ITEM>
